ExtUtils::MakeMaker::Config(3perl)                                                   Perl Programmers Reference Guide                                                   ExtUtils::MakeMaker::Config(3perl)

NAME
       ExtUtils::MakeMaker::Config - Wrapper around Config.pm

SYNOPSIS
         use ExtUtils::MakeMaker::Config;
         print $Config{installbin};  # or whatever

DESCRIPTION
       FOR INTERNAL USE ONLY

       A very thin wrapper around Config.pm so MakeMaker is easier to test.

perl v5.36.0                                                                                    2022-12-12                                                              ExtUtils::MakeMaker::Config(3perl)
